  "doc_id": "59872",
  "text": "The first example that has been implemented (see [CITATION_1] ) in the context of the parareal in time algorithm deals with a differential system for ab initio molecular dynamics simulation. There are many available coarse propagators at our disposal in the literature motivated by physical insight. Very often, these alternative models, of empirical nature depend on coefficients that are fitted to reproduce (to a certain extent) the ab initio models.",
